text: Gabrielle Marie DeLoof (born March 13, 1996) is an American swimmer. She participated at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships, winning a silver medal. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:American female freestyle swimmers Category:World Aquatics Championships medalists in swimming Category:Universiade medalists in swimming Category:Universiade gold medalists for the United States Category:Michigan Wolverines athletes Category:People from Grosse Pointe, Michigan Category:Medalists at the 2019 Summer Universiade
